# rpcProgramVersionMismatch

**Type Property**

The version of the remote procedure call (RPC) program is incorrect.

## Declaration

```swift
static var rpcProgramVersionMismatch: Errno { get }
```

## Discussion

The requested version of the program isn’t available on the remote host.

The corresponding C error is `EPROGMISMATCH`.

## RPC Errors

- **rpcProcedureUnavailable**: Bad procedure for program.
- **rpcProgramUnavailable**: The remote procedure call (RPC) program isn’t available.
- **rpcUnsuccessful**: The structure of the remote procedure call (RPC) is bad.
- **rpcVersionMismatch**: The version of the remote procedure call (RPC) is incorrect.
